data.description: Highlighted by a NEW ROOF installed in 2021, this Aruba floorplan is being offered TURNKEY furnished. Plantation shutters complement the wood floors and crown moldings. Enjoy a spacious kitchen with upgraded stone backsplash and granite counters. The sizeable primary suite features two closets and an en suite bath with dual sinks, a soaker tub, and a walking glass shower. Outside the home is just as impressive. Step out your French doors to an oversized covered and screened lanai. The home is equipped with accordion hurricane shutters. The Cascades just underwent an extensive clubhouse modernization and features pickleball courts, tennis courts, bocce, billiards room, card room, craft space, a library, a large fitness center with a sauna, a satellite pool, a community spa, and a large resort-style pool with indoor/outdoor swimming and a full-time social activities director.
